{"word":"诶","detail":[{"title":"基本字义解释","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"● "},{"type":"strong","content":"诶"},{"type":"strong","content":"（誒）"},{"type":"span","content":"ēi ㄟˉ","class":["pinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 叹词，表示招呼："},{"type":"span","content":"诶","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"，你快看！"}],[{"type":"text","content":"● "},{"type":"strong","content":"诶"},{"type":"strong","content":"（誒）"},{"type":"span","content":"éi ㄟˊ","class":["pinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 叹词，表示诧异："},{"type":"span","content":"诶","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"，你是干什么的！"}],[{"type":"text","content":"● "},{"type":"strong","content":"诶"},{"type":"strong","content":"（誒）"},{"type":"span","content":"ěi ㄟˇ","class":["pinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 叹词，表示不以为然："},{"type":"span","content":"诶","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"，他可不能这么干！"}],[{"type":"text","content":"● "},{"type":"strong","content":"诶"},{"type":"strong","content":"（誒）"},{"type":"span","content":"èi ㄟˋ","class":["pinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 叹词，表示应声或同意："},{"type":"span","content":"诶","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"，就这么办！"}],[{"type":"text","content":"● "},{"type":"strong","content":"诶"},{"type":"strong","content":"（誒）"},{"type":"span","content":"xī ㄒㄧˉ","class":["pinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 叹词，表示可恶、失意而叹惜。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 强笑。"}]]},{"title":"英文翻译","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"an exclamation of confirmation"}]]},{"title":"详细字义解释","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎ "},{"type":"strong","content":"诶"},{"type":"text","content":" 誒 "},{"type":"span","content":"āi","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "}],[{"type":"span","content":"〈动词〉","class":["parts"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1) (形声。从欠,矣声。本义:呵斥)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(2) 同本义"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"诶,訾也。——《说文》。按,实与誒同字"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(3) 叹息"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"乘鄂渚而反顾兮,诶秋冬之绪风。——《楚辞·九章·涉江》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(4)  另见 "},{"type":"span","content":"ǎi;ěi;èi","class":["pinyin"]}]]},{"title":"康熙字典","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"【酉集上】【言字部】誒 "}],[{"type":"text","content":"【唐韻】許其切【集韻】虛其切，"},{"type":"span","content":"𠀤"},{"type":"text","content":"音僖。【說文】可惡之辭。一曰誒然。引春秋傳：誒誒出出。今【左傳·襄三十年】作譆。　又【前漢·韋賢傳】勸誒厥生。【註】誒，歎聲。　又【楚辭·大招】誒笑狂只。【註】誒，猶强也。或曰笑樂也。一作娛。　又誒詒，疑疾。詳前詒字註。　又【玉篇】虛宜切，音羲。又【集韻】呼來切，音咍。又於開切，音哀。又於代切，哀去聲。又於記切，音意。義"},{"type":"span","content":"𠀤"},{"type":"text","content":"同。　【集韻】或作唉。"}]]},{"title":"说文解字","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"【卷三】【言部】"},{"type":"span","content":"誒","class":["kszi"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"可惡之辭。从言矣聲。一曰誒然。《春秋傳》曰：“誒誒出出。”許其切"}]]},{"title":"字源演变","content":[]},{"title":"同音字","content":[]}],"traditional":"誒","type":"生僻字","pinyin":["èi","éi","ĕi","ăi","ēi","éi","ěi","èi"],"radical":"讠","stroke":"七画","total_stroke":"九画","t_radical":"言","t_stroke":"七画","t_total_stroke":"九画","stroke_order":"丶フフ丶ノ一一ノ丶","input_method":{"bopomofo":"IVIOK","number":"33784","unicode":"U+8BF6","wubi":"YCTD"}}